title: Dopefish Cake!
content:
2 years ago, it was a competition in my school - a cake competition. [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-cheeky.gif[/img]
Me and my friends decided to make a Dopefish Cake [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-grin.gif[/img]
The teachers didn't send us the pictures for a very long time, but now when we got it I can finally post it and show it too all the Keen lovers [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-grin.gif[/img]

[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-dopefish.gif[/img]

So here it is:
[img]http://img105.imageshack.us/img105/8515/dopefishcakedf8.jpg[/img]


Remember, we were 12-13 when we made the cake, don't complain [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-dopekeen.gif[/img]
